CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1962, pg. 1 reads:"President Kennedy Stumps Area for Democrats - McKeesport's high school band is shown as it participated in salute to the President."
TitMainTitle: McKeesport High School marching band lining up preparing to march, with sharpshooters on roof tops and billboard for Union Clothing Co., during President Kennedy campaign stop, McKeesport, Pennsylvania
